  # Example bucket policies
  #
  #   policy examples][5] in the *Amazon S3 User Guide*.
  #
  #   **Directory bucket example bucket policies** - See [Example bucket
  #   policies for S3 Express One Zone][6] in the *Amazon S3 User Guide*.
