  #
  #   If you provide an individual checksum, Amazon S3 ignores any provided
  #   `ChecksumAlgorithm` parameter.
  #
  #
  #
  #   [1]: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/userguide/checking-object-integrity.html
  #
