  #   data received is the same data that was originally sent. This header
  #   specifies the Base64 encoded, 160-bit `SHA1` digest of the object. For
  #   more information, see [Checking object integrity][1] in the *Amazon S3
  #   User Guide*.
  #
  #
  #
