  #   | `:complete_multipart_upload` | {Client#complete_multipart_upload} |
  #   | `:abort_multipart_upload`    | {Client#abort_multipart_upload}    |
  #   | `:list_parts`                | {Client#list_parts}                |
  #   | `:upload_part`               | {Client#upload_part}               |
